{
  "texts": [
    "While this carries the risk of hallucinations, the researcher can reduce this risk by verifying that the behaviors and rationales are consistent with one another.",
    "Our application in the following Sections showcases how this can be done in practice.",
    "Moreover, experiments are strictly monitored by university Institutional Review Boards (IRBs) and necessarily constrained from performing a variety of interventions that carry the risk of harming or being unethical.",
    "This phenomenon takes its name from the parable of a drunkard searching for his keys late at night.",
    "He focuses his search underneath a lamp post, since this is \"where the light is\"."
  ]
}